| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2600 — Recovery Inhibition (nitrogen)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e025ea16-0cdb-5b19-a529-8f28f2ca05a5"
